{"tid":36232,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人由細到大都鍾意聽同一個歌手？","createTime":"2016-12-12T14:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T19:11:25.000Z","uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"171d55f095c0a82f2d59f6547f84b5a9243f5e06","tid":36232,"uid":49864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"我係聽廣東歌大，讀書年代聽李克勤，重要係超迷個種。<br />\n<br />\n開始出黎打工就聽 Eason。<br />\n<br />\n依家最鍾意聽麥浚龍。但 Eason 出歌仍然會聽會買；克勤呢？都會聽下，不過通常係聽一次就算個種。<br />\n<br />\n最近有個 fd 問我點解以前鍾意克勤，依家會走去聽 Juno，完全兩個 style。我諗下又係喎，一個係零瑕疵、一個係 &hellip;... （唔想踩我個偶像)<br />\n<br />\n咁有無人由細到大都鍾意聽同一個歌手？"},{"pid":"f09a1a2751a3b6074922251ec3797caed8ffec19","tid":36232,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"Eason<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8840d3a911a4725da7ac8dcb09e4af7181357db1","tid":36232,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:35:55.000Z","msg":"周董"},{"pid":"855506aa05934a8a99c264005a78cd7ceef8dbe8","tid":36232,"uid":22576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"Janice衛蘭"},{"pid":"8bade5d67cd04c8b0bf350dad726a26986e984a3","tid":36232,"uid":7173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"Eason for sure<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9309a548cc92be119a460fa05c0629e68a4b898","tid":36232,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Janice衛蘭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n由佢岀道就開始迷佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09e4b9b0864e45cd76d47175fe9fe480d767447","tid":36232,"uid":19073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T14:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周董</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=